docs {
  # Get Locations by Name

  Retrieves locations matching a name.

  ## Path Parameters
  - `name`: Location name to search for

  ## Query Parameters
  - `activeOnly`: Return only active locations (default: true)

  ## Response
  Returns collection of matching locations.
}

